{"tid":1507714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"開槍警係英勇，咁唔開槍果D係乜？","createTime":"2019-08-26T09:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T10:31:05.000Z","uid":30040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d854bd3a5defac4d0c6fda463ea2b97dd3064cfe","tid":1507714,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:17:55.000Z","msg":"全城關注周日晚荃灣沙嘴道有軍裝警舉槍指向市民，總警司謝振中指，當時有過百名「暴徒」以長鐵支、竹支、路牌等物路攻擊性武器追擊警員，謝表示「暴徒」的目不只僅為追打警員；更是想嚴重傷害、危及警員的性命。謝指早在該批被追擊的警員到場前，已被「泯滅人性暴徒」惡意以削尖的竹支攻擊了一下。謝質疑這還是否和平示威者。謝當時警員在感到生命受威脅、多次警告無效下，並選擇了使用警槍，其中一名警員並向天開了一槍，謝形容開槍警「英勇克制」，指當時使用的武力是必須和合理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為左表示全體警員都係英勇，我認為應該齊齊開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d3cccf749a46fcbff7444eba053388b8f13e23","tid":1507714,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=3fbc8d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"fa0e21d3d27348036db6c1198529b5ebf5534112","tid":1507714,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"其他果D垃圾<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要繼續表揚下開槍果位英勇警察"},{"pid":"2bfcf31f940de969aa0aecb33943619baf1f1c2e","tid":1507714,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa0e21d3d27348036db6c1198529b5ebf5534112","tid":1507714,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"其他果D垃圾<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要繼續表揚下開槍果位英勇警察"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:26:37.000Z","msg":"鼓勵開槍，開槍就係英勇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"